es\"</a>. The China Post. CNA. 16 October 2011<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 August</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Taiwan+Academies+open+in+3+US+cities&amp;rft.date=2011-10-16&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapost.com.tw%2Ftaiwan%2Fforeign-affairs%2F2011%2F10%2F16%2F319974%2FTaiwan-Academies.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATaiwan+Academy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Chen-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Chen_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Chen Hui-ping (2011-11-02). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2011/11/02/2003517276\">\"KMT lawmakers miffed at Taiwan Academy's name\"</a>. Taipei Times<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-05-25</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=KMT+lawmakers+miffed+at+Taiwan+Academy%E2%80%99s+name&amp;rft.date=2011-11-02&amp;rft.au=Chen+Hui-ping&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taipeitimes.com%2FNews%2Ftaiwan%2Farchives%2F2011%2F11%2F02%2F2003517276&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATaiwan+Academy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2012/06/07/2003534728\">\"Academy 'not competing' with PRC\"</a>. Taipei Times. 2012-06-07<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-05-25</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Academy+%E2%80%98not+competing%E2%80%99+with+PRC&amp;rft.date=2012-06-07&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taipeitimes.com%2FNews%2Ftaiwan%2Farchives%2F2012%2F06%2F07%2F2003534728&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATaiwan+Academy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Kuo-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Kuo_7-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Kuo_7-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Kuo, Grace. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20140819082938/http://www.mtsac.edu/presidentsboardreport/Taiwan%20launches%20Taiwan%20Academy%20branches%20in%20US.pdf\">\"Taiwan launches Taiwan Academy branches in US\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. The China Times. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mtsac.edu/presidentsboardreport/Taiwan%20launches%20Taiwan%20Academy%20branches%20in%20US.pdf\">the original</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span> on 2014-08-19<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2014-05-25</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Taiwan+launches+Taiwan+Academy+branches+in+US&amp;rft.aulast=Kuo&amp;rft.aufirst=Grace&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtsac.edu%2Fpresidentsboardreport%2FTaiwan%2520launches%2520Taiwan%2520Academy%2520branches%2520in%2520US.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATaiwan+Academy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mofa.gov.tw/en/News_Content3.aspx?n=4BAF9BD5400A05D9&amp;sms=BA5E856472F10901&amp;s=AD2C0693F4D93654\">\"Foreign Policy Report, 8th Congress of the Legislative Yuan, 4th Session\"</a>. 28 November 2013<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 August</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Foreign+Policy+Report%2C+8th+Congress+of+the+Legislative+Yuan%2C+4th+Session&amp;rft.date=2013-11-28&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mofa.gov.tw%2Fen%2FNews_Content3.aspx%3Fn%3D4BAF9BD5400A05D9%26sms%3DBA5E856472F10901%26s%3DAD2C0693F4D93654&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATaiwan+Academy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-culture-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-culture_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Chang, Chia Chi (1 December 2011). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20140819090747/http://www.culture.tw/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=2189&amp;Itemid=157\">\"Taiwan Academy-- An introduction to the culture of Taiwan\"</a>. <i>Taiwan Culture Portal</i>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.culture.tw/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=2189&amp;Itemid=157\">the original</a> on 19 August 2014<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 August</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Taiwan+Culture+Portal&amp;rft.atitle=Taiwan+Academy--+An+introduction+to+the+culture+of+Taiwan&amp;rft.date=2011-12-01&amp;rft.aulast=Chang&amp;rft.au